(1. Purpose) Tj
T*
(----------) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(This document describes how the Bulgaria real estate platform is intended to work as a) Tj
T*
(continuously running ingestion, normalization, grouping, search, CRM, and publishing system.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(It is meant to be useful for:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(- project owners) Tj
T*
(- operators) Tj
T*
(- Cursor/Codex/Claude agents) Tj
T*
(- backend and frontend developers) Tj
T*
(- future infrastructure and QA work) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
