(2. Product Goal) Tj
T*
(---------------) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(The platform should become a single operational system that:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(1. constantly parses the Bulgarian real estate market and related supply channels) Tj
T*
(2. stores every found listing link and listing snapshot) Tj
T*
(3. normalizes all data into a canonical schema) Tj
T*
(4. compares listings to detect the same apartment or property across multiple sites) Tj
T*
(5. groups duplicate and near-duplicate listings into one property item with multiple source) Tj
T*
(variations) Tj
T*
(6. exposes a list view, property detail view, 3D map view, CRM chat/inbox, settings, and admin) Tj
T*
(tools) Tj
T*
(7. later publishes approved inventory back to supported channels through official or authorized) Tj
T*
(routes) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
